update on 2,3 turing machine

--

This all happened at the end of October, but I am just getting around to checking out the results - and the fallout of the proposed solution.

I first posted about the challenge in:

'nf
<a href=http://www.0x743.com/.vee/1179247100.2007-05-15T12:38:20.html>http://www.0x743.com/.vee/1179247100.2007-05-15T12:38:20.html</a>

